description	"Mira [Scout / Jedi Sentinel]

^2Weaponry:
- Lightsaber
-- Medium Style Only
-- Saber / Blaster Defense (1)
-- Blaster Deflect (1)
-- Cannot Throw Lightsaber
- Blaster Pistol (3)
- 1 Thermal Detonator
- 3 Frag, Cryo, Sonic & Fire Grenades

^6Inventory:
- Electrobinoculars

^5Force Powers:
- Jump  (1)
- Pull  (2)
- Sense (1)
- Blinding (2)

^8Attributes:
- Healing (2)
- Force Block (2)

^3Abilities:
- 3 Poison Darts ^3[CS1]
- Whistling Birds ^3[CS2]
- Grapple Hook (2) ^3[CS3]
- Dodge (3) ^3[CS4]

Mira was a female Human bounty hunter and one of the Lost Jedi from the moon Nar Shaddaa, serving as one of the followers of Meetra Surik. She has already begun the steps to become a jedi, but is still retains her old arsenal, which includes a blaster pistol, wrist launcher, and a large arsenal of explosives."